DHW08_EfficiencyCOP IsPresent And DHW08_EfficiencyCOP == DHW08cc_EfficiencyCOP Or 
DHW08_ThermalEfficiency IsPresent And DHW08_ThermalEfficiency == DHW08cc_ThermalEfficiency Or
DHW08_UniformEnergyFactor IsPresent And DHW08_UniformEnergyFactor == DHW08cc_UniformEnergyFactor Or
DHW08_EnergyFactor IsPresent And DHW08_EnergyFactor == DHW08cc_EnergyFactor
)
And 
