DHW10_WaterHeaterStandbyLossFraction IsPresent And DHW10_WaterHeaterStandbyLossFraction == DHW10cc_WaterHeaterStandbyLossFraction
)
result = ExactMatch
 
Else If 
DHW08_EfficiencyAFUE IsPresent And DHW08_EfficiencyAFUE GTE DHW08cc_EfficiencyAFUE Or 
DHW08_EfficiencyCOP IsPresent And DHW08_EfficiencyCOP GTE DHW08cc_EfficiencyCOP Or 
DHW08_ThermalEfficiency IsPresent And DHW08_ThermalEfficiency GTE DHW08cc_ThermalEfficiency Or
DHW08_UniformEnergyFactor IsPresent And DHW08_UniformEnergyFactor GTE DHW08cc_UniformEnergyFactor Or
DHW08_EnergyFactor IsPresent And DHW08_EnergyFactor GTE DHW08cc_EnergyFactor
)
Or
(
DHW10_StandbyLoss IsPresent And DHW10_StandbyLoss LTE DHW10cc_StandbyLoss Or
DHW10_WaterHeaterStandbyLossFraction IsPresent And DHW10_WaterHeaterStandbyLossFraction LTE DHW10cc_WaterHeaterStandbyLossFraction
)
Or TableWaterMF is Present And DHW01_InstalledSameAsCC == false
result = EqualBetter
