               <xsd:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">Values in this section are affected by data in other sections of the document which may change the result to true and select Yes radio button.  
 
If user changes a required CV value from true to false by selecting the No radio button, an explanation is required in Section E Additional Remarks And D03_ExceptionalConditionMessageCIPLBE += UserChangedNRCVSelection.
