                        <xsd:documentation source="AdditionalRequirements">LMCV-PLB-21-H HERS Verified Multifamily Central Hot Water System Distribution</xsd:documentation>
                        <xsd:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If LMCC-PRF parent
result = Lmcv05_RequireLMCVPlb21H  
If result == true 
